# IdeaVault – Future Ideas

Capture, organize and never lose a great idea again.

---

## About

IdeaVault is a personal idea storage app for iOS. Add titles, 
descriptions, tags and feature breakdowns to every idea — 
all kept privately on your device.

Export your ideas as JSON or Markdown anytime to keep them 
backed up and portable.

